Class AMemoryOperation

        • sg.dex.starfish.impl.memory.AMemoryOperation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Asset, Operation
    public abstract class AMemoryOperation
extends AMemoryAsset
implements Operation
    Class representing a local in-memory operation asset. Operations are executed in a thread pool managed by a MemoryAgent.

    Intended for use in testing or local development situations.

    This is a abstract base class that implements common functionality required for different memory operations. Subclasses only need to override the `compute` method to provide an alternative operation implementation.
